    "description": "<p><strong>STRAITS BUNKERING PTE LTD</strong></p><p><br /></p><p>ESTABLISHED IN 2014, STRAITS BUNKERING PTE LTD FOCUSES ON PROVIDING WORLD CLASS BUNKERING SERVICES TO VESSELS CALLING BOTH SINGAPORE AND MALAYSIAN WATERS.</p><p>STRAITS BUNKERING PTE LTD IS CONSISTENTLY EXPANDING AND NOW WE FULLY OWN 12 MARINE FUEL OIL BARGES AND 2 MARINE GAS OIL BARGES TO FACILITATE BOTH SINGAPORE AND MALAYSIA DELIVERIES.</p><p>ALL OF OUR BARGES ARE STRATEGICALLY STATIONED IN THESE WATERS; SPECIALLY CATERING TO EACH AND EVERY CLIENT’S BUNKER REQUIREMENTS.</p><p>WE ARE HERE TO SERVE YOUR ENERGY NEEDS AND TO BE AVAILABLE FOR YOU 24 HOURS A DAY, 7 DAYS A WEEK, ALL YEAR ROUND, FUELLING THE FUTURE.</p>",
